nodes.text: Mygeeto Burns was a painting depicting a battle between Jedi and LM-432 crab droids on the planet Mygeeto during the Clone Wars.

Mygeeto Burns first appeared in "Celestia Galactica Photografica," a collection of in-universe illustrations by Ryan Church collected in Star Wars: Visionaries, a graphic novel edited by Jeremy Barlow and released on April 2, 2005.
